WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:06.260
The anterior epithelium, here, which will become

2
00:00:06.260 --> 00:00:10.200
a part, here, which is called the cornea, there, you see,

3
00:00:10.780 --> 00:00:16.980
the corneal epithelium, which is therefore a mesenchymal tissue,

4
00:00:18.020 --> 00:00:23.400
whereas the conjunctival tissue, we could say it is an

5
00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:27.820
