26
00:01:24.212 --> 00:01:29.392
Iridology is a reading of the mesodermal

27
00:01:29.392 --> 00:01:30.692
vascular system.

28
00:01:31.492 --> 00:01:36.692
By observing the eye, you can see information about trophic changes

29
00:01:36.692 --> 00:01:38.172
