30
00:01:38.352 --> 00:01:43.812
This is expressed in the iris, which are sensors where they can store, for example,

31
00:01:44.432 --> 00:01:44.932
of sulfur.

32
00:01:45.272 --> 00:01:46.952
We can store a lot of things.

33
00:01:47.512 --> 00:01:51.372
And we can learn to read. There is a mapping of how it will be arranged.

34
00:01:52.282 --> 00:01:54.182
there will be another relationship that will be

35
00:01:54.182 --> 00:01:56.562
important, which is the ciliary processes

