51
00:02:33.173 --> 00:02:37.973
Well, this accommodation system involves this lens, which we call the crystalline lens,

52
00:02:38.213 --> 00:02:43.333
by the ciliary muscles, with the ora serrata; well, we'll see that

53
00:02:43.333 --> 00:02:43.613
later,

54
00:02:44.273 --> 00:02:47.753
which will increase, change the shape

55
00:02:48.424 --> 00:02:53.464
of my lens slightly, to allow the image to integrate

56
00:02:53.464 --> 00:02:55.844
correctly on the retinal plane.

57
00:02:56.344 --> 00:02:59.364
First layer, the sclera.

58
00:02:59.884 --> 00:03:02.564
Second layer, the choroid.

59
00:03:02.784 --> 00:03:04.964
Third layer, the retina.

60
00:03:06.744 --> 00:03:11.244
The nervous tissue, the deepest, which is truly the expression of the brain.

61
00:03:11.684 --> 00:03:16.024
With the colobomatous cleft, which gives rise to the anomaly.

62
00:03:16.495 --> 00:03:22.455
for the hyaloid artery and vessels

63
00:03:22.455 --> 00:03:24.315
